data.description: 3.375% Assumable Loan. Motivated Sellers come with all offers, Structural Warranty Still included until 2028!! **Walk In Closets Galore! This spacious 5 Bedroom Home boasts with 2 living areas, including an oversized loft upstairs, brand new carpet, and freshly painted walls! Comes with water softener, and finished porch with room to expand in this backyard! If you're looking for a quiet neighborhood but still great schools, look no further, tucked away in quiet neighborhood, you'll be just a quick drive to San Antonio or New Braunfels! Wired security transfer available!
